spec_data.Name: fedora-arm-installer
spec_data.Description:
Allows one to first select a source image (local or remote). The image must be
a binary file containing: [MBR + Partitions + File Systems + Data]. A
destination block device should then be selected for final installation.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:05:39 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Writes binary image files to any specified block device
